***Solution 2* - Single traversal (Important concept)**

---

> Now let suppose we have two pointer left and right if we can move left **forward** and right **backward** then our task is going to simpler right 

**To merge we need to write only this much code**
```
Leftnext =  left.next;
left.next =  right;
rigt.next =  Leftnext
